{"tid":1385972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立法會鬼祟滅聲","createTime":"2019-07-30T08:20:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T08:21:12.000Z","uid":117130,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2cf810753a2d082ee4b229096e157905f2770588","tid":1385972,"uid":117130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:20:15.000Z","msg":"之前有秘書處職員喺立法會𨋢入面貼連儂牆，被人秒速撕走。尋日再有職員貼，又係即撕滅聲。立法會仲要即刻加強咗部安，同埋有傳聞話偷偷地裝返之前壞晒cctv。<br />\n<br />\n人哋表下態都唔俾。某人又鬼祟，又小器，令到職員忍無可忍，都話要支持吓嚟緊8月2嘅集會。<br />\n<br />\n如果身邊有公務員或者做立法會嘅朋友，請叫埋佢地一齊join！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/30/161748_42fd5a8b16650300b1dd227926887275.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F30%2F161748_42fd5a8b16650300b1dd227926887275.png&h=5abc3462&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"95ec8381fccbcaf8175d29519350ab6bd6dbc78a","tid":1385972,"uid":144492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:21:12.000Z","msg":"陳維穩最唔政治中立"}]}